	<article class="post-626550 post type-post status-publish hentry category-legal category-mergers-acquisitions tag-corporate-taxes tag-real-estate-investment-trusts tag-tax-shelters tag-united-states-politics-and-government des-corporate-taxes des-real-estate-investment-trusts des-tax-shelters des-united-states-politics-and-government news_keywords-corporate-tax news_keywords-reit news_keywords-tax-shelter news_keywords-us-politics" id="post-626550">
	<header class="postHeader">
